{"tid":2491650,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"麻生太郎:難道太平洋是中國的下水道嗎？","createTime":"2021-04-16T12:48:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-16T13:03:23.000Z","uid":75656,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c239bb32953188d1b1ddd7d85928427a8224362f","tid":2491650,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:48:28.000Z","msg":"日本產經新聞報導，麻生今天在內閣會議後的例行記者會上說：「有人說『太平洋不是日本的下水道』，那難道太平洋是中國的下水道嗎？應該是大家的海才是。」<br />\n<br />\n福島第一核電廠的核廢水經過處理後，會將殘留的輻射物質氚的濃度加以稀釋。若要排放到海洋時，濃度稀釋到世界衛生組織（WHO）飲用水水質指南所規定的1/7的程度。<br />\n<br />\n麻生說：「這點是最重要的。」他認為，日本政府是有科學根據在處理核廢水。<br />\n<br />\n日本政府13日決定兩年後將把東京電力公司福島第一核電廠的處理水排入大海。<br />\n<br />\n麻生13日在內閣會議後的記者會上表示，有科學根據符合標準的話，應該早點將福島核廢水排放入海比較好。他說，要放入大海的福島核廢水含氚濃度比中國、韓國核電廠排入大海的核廢水濃度還低。他還說，經處理稀釋過的福島核廢水即使喝了也沒事。<br />\n<br />\n福島核廢水擬排放入海引起中國反彈。趙立堅14日在中國外交部例行記者會上說：「太平洋不是日本的下水道」。趙立堅表示，如果真如麻生太郎所言，要放入大海的福島核廢水喝了也沒事的話，那麻生就喝喝看。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=926326\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D926326&d=oTLiiFgDV%2FfsDwDkP3XzLQAFq6fDUSnvy6go1IBd1q0%3D&h=30a8dc4f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.setn.com%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3D926326&h=ffe4dae6\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.setn.com/News.aspx?NewsID=926326</a>"},{"pid":"b89213b6c498a2a9d2364711eb31e575c810956d","tid":2491650,"uid":197563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:49:21.000Z","msg":"日本人不吃三文魚"},{"pid":"5865d5a7b730e9d8526b627ab77e6a7e064ec689","tid":2491650,"uid":290118,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:49:48.000Z","msg":"日本仔都唔縮了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42d3a6d52900e0f80dbd836839909a672f80eaa7","tid":2491650,"uid":325556,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:50:18.000Z","msg":"好撚串喎，支持支國打柒日本<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c70338dcff13bbd00ab6777356335e88a8a9ae87","tid":2491650,"uid":112551,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:50:33.000Z","msg":"麻生識玩一定叫趙立堅飲自家廢水"},{"pid":"90a8b4ae564ee0d76357d212abc0c13892e1f161","tid":2491650,"uid":42548,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:51:38.000Z","msg":"駁咀喎, 吓？？!!"},{"pid":"c808ebaf41bfc2b17f4f6281551a9aca74719633","tid":2491650,"uid":41643,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:51:43.000Z","msg":"中國是太平洋的下水道<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14b632c15a9db4e8da5f91cfdec697d543b8dc06","tid":2491650,"uid":299537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:53:26.000Z","msg":"「逼官員飲X水是不能接受的屈辱行為」"},{"pid":"45446fdfc7f38d08cc862a342f8fb167f77de13b","tid":2491650,"uid":256143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:53:36.000Z","msg":"麻生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403679eef27094d8efccc7f4f8dbb7ae6968ec79","tid":2491650,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:56:48.000Z","msg":"雜種下令原神退出日本市場啦，日本仔即刻暴動，到時日本政府頭痕<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ef5a7b8dfb188731fc99da45c0b710e496ecf4","tid":2491650,"uid":261388,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:57:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3cc5d9df6fbf4ef6afb6dcf062b0d0d53adaba1d","tid":2491650,"uid":16719,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-16T12:57:56.000Z","msg":"炮轟小日本啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"063af060e98efa03360171f9a901fffa7ff6bae8","tid":2491650,"uid":266654,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"403679eef27094d8efccc7f4f8dbb7ae6968ec79","tid":2491650,"uid":313162,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"r